Host user@ip
    LocalDirectory /absolute/path/to/local/directory
    RemoteDirectory /absolute/path/to/remote/directory
------------------------------------------------------
in combination with a ssh config file
------------------------------------------------------
Host HostName
    LocalDirectory /absolute/path/to/local/directory
    RemoteDirectory /absolute/path/to/remote/directory
------------------------------------------------------
mount by LocalDirectory
------------------------------------------------------
---
    LocalDirectory /absolute/path/to/local/directory
    RemoteDirectory /absolute/path/to/remote/directory
